OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784031511
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle blaze at
OL,4,Celectricity substation near Sealife
OL,5,CCentre
OL,7,FWeymouth Sealife Centre has shut its
OL,8,Fdoors to visitors today following a
OL,9,Ffire at a nearby electricity
OL,10,Fsubstation.
OL,12,FThe popular tourist attraction
OL,13,Fconfirmed in a statement that, while
OL,14,Fthe blaze did not spread to any of the
OL,15,Faquarium buildings, it will be shut as
OL,16,Fa precaution.
OL,18,FIt said no staff, visitors or animals
OL,19,Fwere injured and that it will re-open
OL,20,Fto the public "once it has been
OL,21,Fconfirmed it is safe to do so".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
