PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784031511
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle blaze at
OL,4,Celectricity substation near Sealife
OL,5,CCentre
OL,7,FFirefighters were called to reports of
OL,8,Fa fire near the town's skatepark on
OL,9,FSunday, with 40 crews in attendance at
OL,10,Fthe height of the blaze.
OL,12,FTwo hose reels, main jets and foam
OL,13,Fwere used to extinguish the fire,
OL,14,Fwhich also caused power to be lost to
OL,15,Faround 100 properties.
OL,17,FFirefighters remained at the scene
OL,18,Fshortly after 7.30pm on Sunday evening
OL,19,Fto dampen down the scene.
